OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1780837873
OL,3,CRoyal Bank of Scotland branch to close
OL,4,Cin Castle Douglas
OL,6,FCastle Douglas' final high street bank
OL,7,Fwill close its doors in September,
OL,8,Fafter Natwest Group announced further
OL,9,Fbranch closures.
OL,11,FThe branch is on of six Royal Bank of
OL,12,FScotland branches earmarked for
OL,13,Fclosure by the group, and will close
OL,14,Fpermanently at midday on 10 September.
OL,16,FFinlay Carson MSP, who represents
OL,17,FGalloway and West Dumfries, says:
OL,18,F"There's been a lot of bank closures
OL,19,Fand I suppose this is going to be felt
OL,20,Fthe hardest, because it leaves no
OL,21,Fbanking facilities.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1780837873
OL,3,CRoyal Bank of Scotland branch to close
OL,4,Cin Castle Douglas
OL,6,F"To have no access for small
OL,7,Fbusinesses, for the elderly, for the
OL,8,Fmost vulnerable in society, they are
OL,9,Fgoing to be left with a 30 maybe a 100
OL,10,Fmile round trip to get to banking
OL,11,Ffacilities."
OL,13,FNatwest Group says it will announce no
OL,14,Ffurther branch closures until 2029,
OL,15,Fand will be investing #50 million over
OL,16,Fthe next year, with a focus on
OL,17,F"modernising existing locations,
OL,18,Fimproving customer experience and
OL,19,Fensuring colleagues are equipped to
OL,20,Fprovide high quality, in person
OL,21,Fsupport."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1780837873
OL,3,CRoyal Bank of Scotland branch to close
OL,4,Cin Castle Douglas
OL,6,FIn a statement, Solange Chamberlain,
OL,7,FCEO, Retail Banking, NatWest Group
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is an important moment for
OL,9,Four customers and the communities we
OL,10,Fserve. We are investing to offer
OL,11,Fcustomers a seamless mix of ways to
OL,12,Fbank with us, including over the
OL,13,Fphone, digitally, or via our free to
OL,14,Fuse ATM network ` while continuing to
OL,15,Fsupport those who prefer face-to-face
OL,16,Fbanking in branches and community
OL,17,Fbanking hubs.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1780837873
OL,3,CRoyal Bank of Scotland branch to close
OL,4,Cin Castle Douglas
OL,6,F"We will not announce any further
OL,7,Fbranch closures until at least 2029
OL,8,Fand are expanding more flexible and
OL,9,Faccessible ways to bank, with enhanced
OL,10,Fsupport to help customers act with
OL,11,Fconfidence and achieve their financial
OL,12,Fgoals.
OL,14,F"We understand the impact these
OL,15,Fchanges can have for our colleagues
OL,16,Fand customers, and we will engage
OL,17,Fpersonally with all those affected by
OL,18,Ftoday's closure announcement."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
